          • de.cuioss.test.jsf.mocks.CuiMockViewHandler
  • public class CuiMockViewHandler
extends org.apache.myfaces.test.mock.MockViewHandler20
    In addition to MockViewHandler20 this extension provides a mocked getViewDeclarationLanguage(FacesContext, String) using EasyMock and a method for dynamically adding Composite-Component: registerCompositeComponent(String, String, UIComponent) Technically they have not other use but being defined.
    Author:
    Oliver Wolff
